[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0583","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0583.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0351","title":"多厂商 FTP 服务器 PASV 模式拒绝服务与未授权数据访问漏洞","description":"FTP 协议 PASV 被动模式存在设计缺陷，远程攻击者可利用竞争条件在合法客户端之前连接至服务器为该客户端开放的临时数据端口，导致未经授权的数据访问和敏感信息窃取。若攻击者抢先占用该数据端口，还可导致合法客户端无法完成数据传输，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多种 FTP 服务器实现，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0351"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.610","remediation":"升级至支持 PASV 地址绑定检查的 FTP 服务器（如 vsftpd 3.0+、ProFTPD 1.3.5+），配置数据端口仅接受与控制连接相同 IP 的连接请求。启用 FTPS（FTP over TLS/SSL，RFC 2228）加密数据通道防止窃听；条件允许时切换到 SFTP/SCP。在服务器上限制 PASV 端口范围为固定区间，并通过防火墙仅允许预期客户端 IP 访问该端口段作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://attrition.org/security/advisory/misc/infowar/iw_sec_01.txt","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3389","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0351","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0351.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8xwf-5pv7-g2w4/GHSA-8xwf-5pv7-g2w4.json","https://github.com/CWE-CAPEC/REST-API-wg/blob/5a8974308ef38e8ee4979e4a29b3b3a22c647822/json_repo/W/421.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82479/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_100_200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000509.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0583.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0485","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0485.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0291","title":"Qbik WinGate 代理默认无密码未授权访问漏洞","description":"WinGate 代理服务器在默认安装时未设置访问密码，导致缺乏必要的身份认证机制。远程攻击者可在无需任何认证的条件下连接至该代理服务，利用其开放的代理功能转发网络连接请求，从而隐藏攻击来源、绕过访问控制或发起匿名攻击。该漏洞影响 WinGate 全系列早期版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0291"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.093","remediation":"立即为 WinGate 代理服务设置管理密码并启用用户认证机制；在 GateKeeper 管理控制台中配置访问控制列表，仅允许受信任的内部 IP 地址段使用代理服务；如业务不需要代理功能，直接卸载或禁用 WinGate 服务；同时在网络防火墙层面拦截外部对 8080/1080 等常见代理端口的入站连接作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0291","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0291.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0291","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0291.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/wingate.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0485.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0591","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0591.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0360","title":"Microsoft Site Server 2.0 任意文件上传漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server 2.0 与 IIS 4.0 存在任意文件上传漏洞，由于服务器未对上传文件类型进行有效过滤，远程攻击者可通过向目标网站上传包含恶意 ASP 脚本的文件，从而在服务器上远程执行任意命令。该漏洞影响部署了 IIS 4.0 的 Microsoft Site Server 2.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0360"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.747","remediation":"建议立即删除 /scripts 目录下的 cpshost.dll、uploadn.asp、uploadx.asp、upload.asp、repost.asp、postinfo.asp 等文件；如无需 Site Server 功能应直接卸载该组件。通过 IIS MMC 管理控制台检查并移除 Web 目录的 Write 写权限。使用 NTFS 文件权限确保匿名 Internet 账户 (IUSR_MACHINE) 对文件系统没有任何写入权限。鉴于该产品已停止支持，建议升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本及 IIS。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91763097004101&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20305","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0360.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0360","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0360.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0360.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jrg6-c727-f24w/GHSA-jrg6-c727-f24w.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0360.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/iis_repost_asp.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0591.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0717","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0717.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0461","title":"Linux/Unix rpcbind 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Linux、IRIX 及 Wietse Venema 实现的 rpcbind（RPC 端口映射服务）存在认证缺陷，远程攻击者无需任何身份验证即可向目标系统发送伪造源地址的 RPC 请求，从而在 rpcbind 中插入或删除服务条目，导致服务注册信息被篡改，可能进一步用于中间人攻击或劫持 RPC 调用。该漏洞影响多个 Unix 类系统的 rpcbind 组件，CVSS v2 评分 10.0，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0461"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.697","remediation":"立即升级 rpcbind 软件包至最新版本（Linux 发行版如 Red Hat 可使用 `yum update rpcbind`，Debian/Ubuntu 使用 `apt upgrade rpcbind`）。同时配置 iptables 防火墙规则仅允许信任 IP 访问 UDP/TCP 111 端口，或在 `/etc/hosts.allow` 中添加 `portmap: 信任网段`、`/etc/hosts.deny` 中添加 `portmap: ALL` 限制来源。如无需使用 NFS/RPC 服务，建议直接关闭 rpcbind 服务（`systemctl disable rpcbind && systemctl stop rpcbind`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0461"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0717.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0573","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0573.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0349","title":"Microsoft IIS FTP LIST 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 的 FTP 服务中的 list (ls) 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的 FTP 列表请求触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响早期版本的 IIS，攻击条件低，危害严重，建议及时安装安全补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0349"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.357","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-003 提供的补丁（Q223783），或升级至 IIS 5.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中禁用 FTP 服务（停止 MSFTPSVC 服务），或限制匿名用户对 FTP 根目录的写入权限以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ188348","http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/IIS%20Remote%20FTP%20Exploit/DoS%20Attack.html","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-003","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0349","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0349.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hcx3-7fvg-jr7j/GHSA-hcx3-7fvg-jr7j.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0349.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/iis_ftp_crash.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0573.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0571","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0571.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0348","title":"Microsoft IIS ASP 缓存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Information Server (IIS) 的 ASP 缓存机制存在信息泄露漏洞。当两个虚拟服务器共享同一物理目录时，ASP 脚本缓存未能正确隔离不同虚拟服务器之间的数据，导致攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制请求，获取同一物理目录下其他虚拟站点的敏感信息。该漏洞影响多个 IIS 版本，公开利用难度较低，可能导致网站配置文件、源代码等敏感数据泄露，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0348"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.237","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft KB Q197003 安全更新（包含于 Windows NT 4.0 Security Rollup Package），该更新修复了 ASP 脚本缓存在虚拟服务器间的隔离问题。如无法安装补丁，应将每个虚拟服务器配置为使用独立的物理目录，避免不同虚拟主机共用同一目录；也可在 IIS 管理控制台中禁用 ASP 脚本文件缓存作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ197003","http://www.osvdb.org/930","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0348","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0348.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q6hg-qxrw-r3f8/GHSA-q6hg-qxrw-r3f8.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0348.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0571.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0688","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0688.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0450","title":"Microsoft IIS 5.0 IISAPI扩展根目录枚举漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 5.0 存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务器发送特制的非存在 URL 请求，该请求由 Perl 解释器（perl.exe）处理，从而枚举 Web 服务器根目录下的真实路径。该漏洞影响 Windows 2000 上的 IIS 5.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，导致敏感路径信息泄露，为后续攻击提供侦察支持。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0450"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.340","remediation":"该漏洞存在于 Windows 2000 内置的 IIS 5.0，微软已停止支持该操作系统，根本修复方案是升级至 Windows Server 2012 R2 或更高版本（IIS 8.5+）。临时缓解措施：在 IIS 管理器中删除或取消 scripts 虚拟目录下 perl.exe 的执行权限（属性→执行权限改为\"无\"），并禁用所有非必需的 ISAPI Web 服务扩展。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/194","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19152"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0688.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0688.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0688.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0685","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0685.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0449","title":"Microsoft IIS 4 ExAir 示例网站拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IIS 4.0 附带的 ExAir 示例站点中存在拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证，通过直接向 advsearch.asp、query.asp 或 search.asp 等脚本发送特制 HTTP 请求，即可触发服务端 CPU 资源耗尽，导致正常服务不可用。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 上运行的所有 IIS 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0449"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.213","remediation":"删除 IIS 4.0 中 `\\InetPub\\wwwroot\\ExAir` 目录下的 advsearch.asp、query.asp、search.asp 文件或直接移除整个 ExAir 示例站点目录；同时在 IIS 管理器中删除 ExAir 虚拟目录。生产环境应始终移除所有示例应用程序，并升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）及对应 IIS 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/2","http://www.osvdb.org/3","http://www.osvdb.org/4","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/193"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0685.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0569","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0569.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0347","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer Invalid Byte 跨框架访问漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.01 及 5.0.1 版本中存在跨帧访问安全漏洞，远程攻击者通过在 \"about:\" JavaScript URL 中插入 \"%01\" 无效字节字符，可绕过同源策略限制，跨域读取目标系统本地文件内容或实施网页伪造欺骗。该漏洞影响面广泛，攻击者只需诱使用户访问构造的恶意网页即可触发，无需任何身份认证，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0347"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.110","remediation":"升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 Service Pack 1 或更高版本（如 IE 5.5/6.0），以消除 %01 字符跨域访问漏洞。若无法升级，可临时将 Internet 区域安全级别设为\"高\"并禁用 Active Scripting，以降低被利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91745430007021&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91756771207719&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19156","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0347.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0347","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0347.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0347.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mpqm-r86r-845w/GHSA-mpqm-r86r-845w.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0347.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000498.txt","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0569.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0569.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0569.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0589","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0589.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0357","title":"Microsoft Windows 98 畸形 oshare 数据包远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 98 等操作系统在处理特制的 \"oshare\" 数据包时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送包含无效分片偏移量的恶意网络数据包，触发系统资源耗尽或崩溃，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 98 及可能存在类似问题的其他操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0357"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.350","remediation":"Windows 98 已终止支持，无官方补丁。建议在网络边界防火墙或路由器上过滤入站异常分片报文（drop invalid fragments），阻止恶意「oshare」数据包到达目标主机。若业务允许，应尽快升级至仍受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11）并安装最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0357","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0357","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0357.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3x5w-w876-g26g/GHSA-3x5w-w876-g26g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0589.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0584","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0584.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0352","title":"ControlIT（又名 Remotely Possible）弱密码加密漏洞","description":"ControlIT 4.5 及更早版本（又名 Remotely Possible）存在弱密码加密漏洞，其加密算法强度不足，导致存储在系统配置中的凭据可被轻易破解。远程攻击者若能够访问受影响系统的配置文件或通过网络嗅探获取加密后的密码，可通过逆向分析加密算法还原明文凭据，进而获取系统控制权。该漏洞影响 ControlIT 4.5 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0352"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.740","remediation":"建议立即升级 ControlIT 至 4.5 以上版本（若厂商已停止支持，应迁移至 Symantec pcAnywhere 或当前仍在维护的远程控制方案）。同时启用强密码策略，避免使用短于 8 位的密码，并限制远程访问来源 IP 以减少爆破风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0352"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0584.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0267","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0267.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0121","title":"CDE dtaction 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"dtaction 是 CDE（通用桌面环境）工具集中的命令执行组件，其存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 dtaction 提交超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 CDE 的多款 Unix 系统（包括 Solaris、HP-UX、AIX 等），CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布补丁修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0121"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.013","remediation":"立即移除 dtaction 二进制文件的 setuid root 权限：`chmod 0555 /usr/dt/bin/dtaction`，阻断本地普通用户以 root 权限执行。若业务允许，建议禁用 CDE 桌面环境（`/etc/init.d/dtlogin stop && chkconfig dtlogin off` 或相应平台等价操作）。各 Unix 厂商补丁：Solaris 安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00192 对应补丁 (patch ID 107021-01+)；HP-UX 安装 HPSBUX9909-103 对应补丁；AIX 安装 APAR IY08886 补丁；IRIX 升级至 6.5.15 或更高版本。同时限制可登录系统的本地用户范围，防止非受信用户获得交互式 shell 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0121"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0267.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0690","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0690.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0451","title":"Linux Kernel 2.0 TCP 端口拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.0.36 存在 TCP 端口拒绝服务漏洞。本地用户可通过向非特权端口发送特制请求，阻止任何服务器程序在非特权端口上进行监听，导致系统无法正常启动相关网络服务，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞需要本地用户权限才能利用，攻击复杂度低，影响系统可用性。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0451"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.460","remediation":"升级到 Linux 内核 2.2 及以上版本。对于 Linux 2.0.x 系统，建议升级至 2.0.37 或更高修订版本。当前所有主流发行版早已停止支持 2.0 系列内核，建议完整升级至现代发行版以彻底修复此问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/343","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19271"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0690.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0265","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0265.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0119","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 共享资源未授权访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 beta 版本存在权限验证缺陷，由于系统对共享资源的访问控制机制不完善，任意用户无需身份认证即可读取或删除网络共享目录中的文件。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 beta 测试版系统，攻击者可通过 SMB 协议远程访问目标主机上的共享资源，导致敏感信息泄露或数据丢失，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0119"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.760","remediation":"立即升级 Windows NT 4.0 beta 至 Windows NT 4.0 RTM 正式版，并安装最新 Service Pack 6a。为所有共享目录设置明确的 ACL 权限，禁止 Everyone 组具有读写权限，将共享目录所在分区转换为 NTFS 文件系统以启用更细粒度的访问控制，同时在注册表中将 RestrictAnonymous 键值设置为 1 以限制匿名访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/11"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0265.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1016","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1016.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0678","title":"Debian GNU/Linux Apache HTTPd 默认配置信息泄露漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 2.1 系统中 Apache HTTP Server 的默认配置将 ServerRoot 设置为 /usr/doc 目录，导致 Web 服务器暴露了系统文档文件目录。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过 HTTP 请求访问服务器上本不应公开的敏感文档信息，造成信息泄露。该漏洞源于默认安装时 Apache 配置文件（httpd.conf）中对 ServerRoot 路径的不安全设置，使得 /usr/doc 目录下的全部文档对 Web 访问者可见。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0678"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.777","remediation":"修改 Apache 配置文件 `/etc/apache/httpd.conf`，将 `ServerRoot \"/usr/doc\"` 改为 `ServerRoot \"/etc/apache\"`，并重启 Apache 服务。同时升级至 Debian 2.1 官方补丁版本或更高版本（如 Debian 3.0+），或通过 `chmod 755 /usr/doc` 限制文档目录可读性作为临时缓解。配置完成后使用 `apachectl configtest` 验证语法正确性。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/318","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19253","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0678.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/da16c0690c2898f8d5843973d80d69e9e6a006ba/1999/CVE-1999-0678.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0678","https://github.com/ycdxsb/PocOrExp_in_Github/blob/6b847f7353f402229d68b5fa385edb629370a404/1999/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0678.json","https://github.com/openbmc/openbmc/blob/0b18b8aa47f54da5cd4dec404a8ce498fcdd1173/upstream-layers/meta-openembedded/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/d9905eb7656178d3e59e0bf8f1d53a9ee9e50186/unittests/scans/openvas/many_vuln.xml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0678.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4425-83hj-m78v/GHSA-4425-83hj-m78v.json","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/templates/openvas/reports/generic_report.html","https://github.com/lto7777777/CVE-1999-0678"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1016.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1016.toml"}]